"i Umukoresha Kuri Kugaragaza i Gushyiramo na Gukuramo Amabwiriza ya:  A "
"APAREYE , Nka Nka i Agashushondanga Byakoreshejwe Kuri . Ibisobanuro: ku "
"Amabwiriza Byabonetse ku i Ipaji: ya:  <application> Gushyiramo </"
"application> ( Ubwoko: <userinput> <command> </command> <option> Gushyiramo "
"</option> </userinput> Ku i command Urwinjiriro ) . "

